    • Constructor Detail

      • LoggedKey

        protected LoggedKey(long flyingTime,
         boolean longPress,
         boolean error,
         int orientation,
         double pressure,
         double xAxis,
         double yAxis,
         double zAxis,
         double accX,
         double accY,
         double accZ)
        LoggedKey constructor with logged values.
        Parameters:
        flyingTime - time between last touch and this touch
        longPress - boolean if key was long pressed (for key substitution)
        error - boolean if delete key was pressed
        orientation - orientation of display (up, right, left)
        pressure - pressure of key (works in API less than 14)
        xAxis - orientation X axis
        yAxis - orientation Y axis
        zAxis - orientation Z axis
        accX - accelerator X axis
        accY - accelerator Y axis
        accZ - accelerator Z axis
